Remediations.Description: Go Gold today to take advantage of exclusive Xbox discounts, special deals, and offers.

LocalizedProperties.ProductDescription:
** Xbox One or Xbox 360 (or compatible) controller is required to play.
** Please remember that Windows Firewall must be turned on to enjoy all Xbox Live features.

The eSport classic is now on Windows 10! #IDARB requires an Xbox Live account and an Xbox compatible controller to play.

Prepare to battle everything from Moustache Cops to Breakfast, in this game inspired by fast action, 8-bit sports and arcade classics! Built with the input of thousands of crazed internet gamers, #IDARB is a chaotic 8-player eSport jumping future arena ball game. Create characters, teams, team logos, tournaments, even your theme music, in this highly customizable experience complete with disruptive “hashbombs” which dynamically change the game itself via Twitch and Twitter! IDARB supports up to a whopping 8 simultaneous local players, and up to 4 vs. 4, head-to-head online matches. Additional features include a mind-blowing single-player story mode, wild half time competitions, and unlockable recipes.

Begun as a crowd-sourced project, the game’s title is an acronym for “It Draws a Red Box” (IDARB). Thanks to thousands of suggestions via social media, the game evolved from one red box into the wacky amalgam it is today, complete with hundreds of strange “hashbombs”, secret commands which, when sent to the game via Twitch or Twitter, will disrupt and dynamically change the game in realtime! If there’s something you want that isn’t in #IDARB, it’s probably because you didn’t suggest it, but with so many customization options, you can probably still make it yourself!

Features: Online Mulitplayer Cross-Play with Xbox One version! (Windows Firewall & Xbox Live Account Required)
Up to 8 players on one computer! Or 4 vs 4 over two computers! (Controllers Required)
Hashbombs! Your friends can troll your game live via Twitter (@idarbwire) or Twitch from any device - try #bomb, #clown, #fireworks (and more!)
Make your own players, assemble your own teams, wave your own flags, and even compose your own fight songs
Share your unique creations with your friends via QR codes or the Trading Post
Play in three different base arenas: Arena City, Breakfast Stadium, or Mustache Cops vs Cthulhu in Space!
Expand your play with the ALL NEW Walking Dead / Invincible and Masters of the Universe™ Expansion Packs!
Compete against friends in the new Half-Time Olympics Mode!
LocalizedProperties.RecommendedNotes: Core i5 Processor or better;4GB RAM;Requires Xbox One or Xbox 360 (or compatible) Controller to play;Requires Xbox Live Account & Windows Firewall Enabled
